<br>
1. Enamaled Black chest piece 200p<br>
2. All other slots fill with bronze or banded 100p<br>
3. Crystalized Blade 1hs 100p<br>
4. Any cheap 2hs, just to keep skills up till you hit lvl 20<br>
5. Cheap shield from vendor or shinny brass shield. 10p<br>
<br>
Ears and ring slots I'd ignore unless you can pick up jagged bands or some HP items.<br>
<br>
On weapons, you have a damage cap untill you hit lvl 20, which is limited to the weapons damage rating of 14. In other words untill your lvl 20,  a 14 25 weapon will perform the same as a 50 25 weapon. (verants futile anti-twinking atempt). So go for the best ratio you can find with a damage rating around 14. After lvl 20 go for weapons with high damage and a decent ratio. Post 20 a mithril 2 handed sword rocks for around 300p.<br>
<br>
<br>
